a-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vjc1665702714625.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vjc1665702714625.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vjc1665702714625.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vjc1665702714625\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Window/App </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property defines an associative list of application shell properties. The\n      available properties depend on the type of application shell. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vjc1665702714625__section_w1109ab1b5b1_w1110ab1b5_w1111ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10925e1_d10926e1_d10927e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Technical Name:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n                            WINPROP</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Expected Value:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Associative list of properties and values.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Default Value:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vjc1665702714625__section_tsk_t2k_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1083640e114\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vjc1665702714625__p_d97382e1_d97383e1_d97384e1\">The window properties are the widget properties of a\n            form component. Selected properties can be set in ProcScript using\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$windowproperties</span>. For more\n            information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ryt1665702577808.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ryt1665702577808.html\" title=\"Creates a new instance of a component.\">newinstance</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vjc1665702714625__section_e3h_x2k_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1083640e136\">Windows APS Properties</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Window Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Property</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Technical Property Name</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwc1665702587483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwc1665702587483.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the object.\">Background Color (BackColor)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackColor</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kno1665702715076.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kno1665702715076.html\" title=\"Window property that determines whether the form window has a title bar. Valid values: True (default) or False.\">Caption</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Caption</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fym1665702715516.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fym1665702715516.html\" title=\"Window property of an application shell that determines how the application window is closed.\">Close (CanClose) [APS]</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">CanClose</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dvg1665702715374.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dvg1665702715374.html\" title=\"Determines whether the application window is treated as a Microsoft Windows dialog box, so the window is not resizable.\">Dialog</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Dialog</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cwr1665702715216.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cwr1665702715216.html\" title=\"Window property that determines whether the user can minimize the form or application window at run time, and enables the Minimize/Restore button in the title bar.\">Iconize (CanIconize)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">CanIconize</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qkn1665702715286.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qkn1665702715286.html\" title=\"Determines whether the user can maximize and restore the size of the form or application window using the Maximize/Restore button in the title bar.\">Maximize</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">CanZoom</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gqy1665702715592.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gqy1665702715592.html\" title=\"Determines whether all forms that are run in the application shell are maximized.\">Maximized Forms</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">MaximizedForms</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wjh1665702607394.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wjh1665702607394.html\" title=\"The MessageLine property determines whether the message line is displayed at the bottom of the application window. This is used to display non-obtrusive messages to the user.\">Message Line</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">MessageLine</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kjr1676877187333.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kjr1676877187333.html\" title=\"Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the window can be resized at runtime.\">Resizable (CanResize)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">CanResize</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hse1665702715007.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hse1665702715007.html\" title=\"Determines whether the Uniface Setup utility is available from the system menu in the title bar.\">Setup</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Setup</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ecw1665702715443.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ecw1665702715443.html\" title=\"Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the Windows system menu and buttons to minimize, maximize, and close the window are available for this window. Valid values: True or False.\">System Menu (SysMenu)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10928e1_d10929e1_d10930e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">SysMenu</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10931e1_d10932e1_d10933e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Image Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10931e1_d10932e1_d10933e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Property</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10931e1_d10932e1_d10933e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Technical Property Name</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10931e1_d10932e1_d10933e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"scc1665702611448.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scc1665702611448.html\" title=\"Image used as background for the application window, form, or entity. This property can be set in ProcScript.\">Background Image (BackImage)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10931e1_d10932e1_d10933e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackImage</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10931e1_d10932e1_d10933e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kmv1665702611521.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kmv1665702611521.html\" title=\"This property determines how the data (text or image) is aligned in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Horizontal Alignment (Halign)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10931e1_d10932e1_d10933e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">HAlign</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10931e1_d10932e1_d10933e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gvp1665702611605.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gvp1665702611605.html\" title=\"This property determines the vertical alignment of data (text or image) in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Vertical Alignment ( Valign)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10931e1_d10932e1_d10933e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">VAlign</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10931e1_d10932e1_d10933e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dbd1665702611680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbd1665702611680.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is horizontally scaled; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10931e1_d10932e1_d10933e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Hscale</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10931e1_d10932e1_d10933e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sup1665702611757.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sup1665702611757.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is scaled vertically; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Vertical Scaling ( Vscale)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10931e1_d10932e1_d10933e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">VScale</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10931e1_d10932e1_d10933e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yxe1665702611833.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yxe1665702611833.html\" title=\"Determines whether the aspect ratio of the image is preserved at all times. True (default) or False.\">Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vjc1665702714625__table_d10931e1_d10932e1_d10933e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">PreserveAspect</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vjc1665702714625__section_ert_ggk_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1083640e567\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vjc1665702714625__ul_nyj_jgk_4wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vjc1665702714625__li_d39572e1_d39573e1_d39574e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"quf1665702550125.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/quf1665702550125.html\" title=\"An Application Shell is a Main Development Object that defines the main executable component of an application (Windows or character-based) or application server.\">Application Shell</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616521\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616521\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Window/App Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Window/App This property defines an associative list of application shell properties. The available properties depend on the type of application shell. Technical Name: WINPROP Expected Value: Associative list of properties and values. Default Value: None Description The window properties are the widget properties of a form component. Selected properties can be set in ProcScript using newinstance and $windowproperties . For more information, see newinstance . Windows APS Properties Table 1. Window Properties Property Technical Property Name Background Color (BackColor) BackColor Caption Caption Close (CanClose) [APS] CanClose Dialog Dialog Iconize (CanIconize) CanIconize Maximize CanZoom Maximized Forms MaximizedForms Message Line MessageLine Resizable (CanResize) CanResize Setup Setup System Menu (SysMenu) SysMenu Table 2. Image Properties Property Technical Property Name Background Image (BackImage) BackImage Horizontal Alignment (Halign) HAlign Vertical Alignment ( Valign) VAlign Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale) Hscale Vertical Scaling ( Vscale) VScale Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect) PreserveAspect Applies To Application Shell Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}